Description: # TKlighter
        Adds syntax highlighting to the tkinter Text widget
        
        ## Usage
        
        TKlighter.def_h(text_widget, '#ff0000)
        
        def ekey(event):
            TKlighter.def_h(Tk.Text 'green')
        
        root.bind('<Key-e>', ekey)
        
        
        ## Supports regex
        
            TKlighter.custom_regex_h(e_text, r'de', 'green')
        
        
        
        
